    {
      "id": "short-mechanism",
      "durationMs": 26500,
      "narration": {
        "text": "There is no URL-in-constructor subclassing trap from the old API; the connection is an object you hold. send(...) has a String and a byte[] overload, getReadyState() returns a WebSocketState, and close() does a clean close handshake."
      },
